content.rendered:
Directed by Tigmanshu Dhulia

Written by Tigmanshu Dhulia

Cast Sanjay Dutt (Uday Pratap Singh). Jimmy Shergill (Aditya Pratap Singh). Mahie Gill (Madhvi Devi). Chitrangda Singh (Suhani). Kabir Bedi (Maharaja Hari Singh). Deepak Tijori (Vijay Singh). Pamela Singh Bhutoria (Deepal (as Pamela Bhutoria)). Soha Ali Khan (Ranjana- Special Appearance). Nafisa Ali (Rajmata Yashodhra). Deepraj Rana (Kanhaiya). Zakir Hussain (Bunny Uncle). Manas Thakkar (Shobhit). Rishina Kandhari (Panchali- Uday’s wife). Kanika Dang(Badi Raani- Uday’s mother). Imran Hasnee (Bashir Ali). Alexx O’Nell (Stephen). Jahangir Khan (Mahavat).Kumar Kanchan Ghosh.Ramji Bali.Puja Jha. Gary Tantony (Lord Bailey) . Ajoy Chakraborty (Shashikant Shukla). Rahul Mittra (Mahender pratap Singh). Mayur Sharma (Mayur). Rocky Singh (Rocky). Pankaz Singh Tanwar (Reporter)

Language Hindi

Producers Sankalp Acharekar. Prashant Asawa. Tigmanshu Dhulia. Dharmindra K. Mehra. Rahul Mittra. Gaurav Nanda. Ajay Rai. Rahul Rawat

Production Jar Picture. Rahul Mittra Film
